05049812-e814-481d-9d89-8fbca4b4281d.title: Sedridor
05049812-e814-481d-9d89-8fbca4b4281d.text:
Welcome adventurer, to the world renowned
Wizards' Tower. How may I help you?

options.text: Nothing thanks, I'm just looking around.
What are you doing down here?

e1a94b5f-2114-46aa-ae76-0351cafa5eef.title: <player>
e1a94b5f-2114-46aa-ae76-0351cafa5eef.text: Nothing thanks, I'm just looking around.

80028fdb-17a3-4479-abc0-b0e2da62cbd3.title: Sedridor
80028fdb-17a3-4479-abc0-b0e2da62cbd3.text:
Well, take care adventurer. You stand on the
ruins of the old destroyed Wizards' Tower.
Strange and powerful magicks lurk here.

670a02b0-2bdf-4448-b62b-f0521a12ee45.title: <player>
670a02b0-2bdf-4448-b62b-f0521a12ee45.text: What are you doing down here?

c10c7e67-6362-4658-9d5b-dc6a0580e3ab.title: Sedridor
c10c7e67-6362-4658-9d5b-dc6a0580e3ab.text:
That is indeed a good question. Here in the cellar
of the Wizards' Tower you find the remains of
the old Wizards' Tower, destroyed by fire

f2213203-194f-45f6-80f8-64bc203a1b5c.title: Sedridor
f2213203-194f-45f6-80f8-64bc203a1b5c.text:
many years past by the treachery of the Zamorakians.
Many mysteries were lost, which we try to find once
more. By building this Tower on the remains of the old,

9551c384-b7d8-4025-91ba-1f29c3cd59b1.title: Sedridor
9551c384-b7d8-4025-91ba-1f29c3cd59b1.text:
we sought to show the world of our dedication to
learning the mysteries of Magic. I am here searching
through these fragments for knowledge from
the artefacts from our past.

bf18f61e-9359-4132-b838-a214c2d48a55.title: <player>
bf18f61e-9359-4132-b838-a214c2d48a55.text: And have you found anything useful?

087f32ae-cd6c-4bac-a39f-a1ca7eed7f31.title: Sedridor
087f32ae-cd6c-4bac-a39f-a1ca7eed7f31.text:
Aaaah... that would be telling adventurer. Anything I
have found I cannot speak freely of, for fear the
treachery of the past might be repeated.

options.text: Ok, well I'll leave you to it.

c4fa50cc-63f3-4e5e-a64e-a129ea1ce687.title: Sedridor
c4fa50cc-63f3-4e5e-a64e-a129ea1ce687.text:
Well, it is a long story from the past... Many years
ago, this Wizards' Tower was a focus of great
learning, as we mages studied together to try
and learn the secrets behind

82a277cd-048b-4b4a-8c06-5a771fba5e36.title: Sedridor
82a277cd-048b-4b4a-8c06-5a771fba5e36.text:
the Rune Stones that allow us to use Magic. Who
makes them? Where do they come from? How many
types are there? What spells can they produce? All
these questions and more are still unknown to us,

b0e3b388-8258-4145-93f9-d23797bece9b.title: Sedridor
b0e3b388-8258-4145-93f9-d23797bece9b.text:
but were once known to our ancestors. Legends
tell us that in the past the mages who lived
here could fashion Rune Stones almost at
will, and as many as they desired.

ba10c974-7ef8-4bf4-8c6f-e9c4f377197a.title: Sedridor
ba10c974-7ef8-4bf4-8c6f-e9c4f377197a.text:
No, unfortunately not. Many years past, the
Wizards who follow Zamorak, the god of chaos, burned
this Tower to the ground, and all who were inside.

35bfe68a-0e13-482b-99b7-6acd9d9c18ae.title: Sedridor
35bfe68a-0e13-482b-99b7-6acd9d9c18ae.text:
To this day we do not fully know why they did this
terrible act, but all our research, all of our greatest
magical minds were destroyed in one fell swoop.

5a358185-aace-4094-a061-dcc057dbd14e.title: Sedridor
5a358185-aace-4094-a061-dcc057dbd14e.text:
This is why I spend my time searching through
these few remains we have left from the glorious old
Tower. I hope someday to find something that will
tell us once more of the mysteries of

b1c6cf49-d18f-4c85-b200-f25bdb2953db.title: Sedridor
b1c6cf49-d18f-4c85-b200-f25bdb2953db.text:
the runes that we use daily, which dwindle in supply
with each use. Someday I hope we may once more
create our own runes, and the Wizards' Tower will
once more be a place of glory!

ef7cca12-1250-4f10-9ba9-cb210ec63cd6.title: <player>
ef7cca12-1250-4f10-9ba9-cb210ec63cd6.text: Ok, well I'll leave you to it.

c801cb1c-47ec-48a8-88bd-841e20300a4f.title: Sedridor
c801cb1c-47ec-48a8-88bd-841e20300a4f.text: Perhaps I will see you later <player>.

2271882a-30c6-4270-83c1-5331613aab04.title: <player>
2271882a-30c6-4270-83c1-5331613aab04.text: How did you know my name???

aa8ff4da-a9a8-4cb0-b5be-3dc9826bc882.title: Sedridor
aa8ff4da-a9a8-4cb0-b5be-3dc9826bc882.text: Well, I AM the head wizard here...

7a6a7365-6099-41f6-b135-fd22c2bfa7d9.title: Sedridor
7a6a7365-6099-41f6-b135-fd22c2bfa7d9.text:
Welcome adventurer, to the world renowned
Wizards' Tower. How may I help you?

options.text: Nothing thanks, I'm just looking around.
What are you doing down here?
I'm looking for the head wizard.

432a033d-e2b3-44a9-8453-ea6ddeef6c30.title: <player>
432a033d-e2b3-44a9-8453-ea6ddeef6c30.text: I'm looking for the head wizard.

a992fe3a-5f80-432b-b57f-f1b67852ddbb.title: Sedridor
a992fe3a-5f80-432b-b57f-f1b67852ddbb.text:
Oh, you are, are you?
And just why would you be doing that?

cf601c39-2469-4cb9-9b56-863d49e2e82b.title: <player>
cf601c39-2469-4cb9-9b56-863d49e2e82b.text:
The Duke of Lumbridge sent me to find him. I have
this weird talisman he found. He said the head wizard
would be very interested in it.

3c68ed29-7023-4882-bf9e-605a867b6b63.title: Sedridor
3c68ed29-7023-4882-bf9e-605a867b6b63.text:
Did he now? HmmmMMMMMmmmmm.
Well that IS interesting. Hand it over then adventurer,
let me see what all the hubbub about it is.
Just some amulet I'll wager.

options.text: No, I'll only give it to the head wizard.

557821c5-7bdc-4ee8-b53e-6957ab6fe40b.title: <player>
557821c5-7bdc-4ee8-b53e-6957ab6fe40b.text: No, I'll only give it to the head wizard.

2d00ea40-a16e-4d2e-a6fd-5d4424a464d1.title: Sedridor
2d00ea40-a16e-4d2e-a6fd-5d4424a464d1.text:
HA HA HA HA HA! I can tell you are new to this
land, for I AM the head wizard! Hand it over and
let me have a proper look at it, hmmm?

options.text: No, I don't think you are the head wizard.

fad0c2c7-22ed-4b68-b284-4c4000f3b68b.title: <player>
fad0c2c7-22ed-4b68-b284-4c4000f3b68b.text: No, I don't think you are the head wizard.

f0eb56fc-b36e-4511-89a6-f5cc139c694e.title: Sedridor
f0eb56fc-b36e-4511-89a6-f5cc139c694e.text:
Hmmm. Well, I admire your caution adventurer,
perhaps I can prove myself? I will use my mental
powers to discover...

5d30c97a-275d-4d98-9a7e-4d222cd7f127.title: Sedridor
5d30c97a-275d-4d98-9a7e-4d222cd7f127.text:
Well I am head wizard you know! You don't get to my
position without learning a few tricks along the way!

8850a72f-9655-40ea-b1d3-bcc200170160.title: Sedridor
8850a72f-9655-40ea-b1d3-bcc200170160.text:
So now I have proved myself to you why don't
you hand over that talisman, hmm?

2f4e8346-198b-4f49-8e60-589d6b7af579.title: Sedridor
2f4e8346-198b-4f49-8e60-589d6b7af579.text:
Th-this talisman you brought me...! It is the last piece
of the puzzle, I think! Finally! The legacy of our
ancestors... it will return to us once more!

d5d9a07b-4a97-4e3a-b4fa-6c3143c98682.title: Sedridor
d5d9a07b-4a97-4e3a-b4fa-6c3143c98682.text:
I need time to study this, <player>. Can you please
do me this task while I study this talisman you have
brought me? In the mighty town of Varrock, which

dec38a17-836d-4de1-994e-63544c96f442.title: Sedridor
dec38a17-836d-4de1-994e-63544c96f442.text:
is located North East of here, there is a certain shop
that sells magical runes. I have in this package all of the
research I have done relating to the Rune Stones, and

193f8f97-83d3-4342-aebc-5e21aa90dcde.title: Sedridor
193f8f97-83d3-4342-aebc-5e21aa90dcde.text:
require somebody to take them to the shopkeeper so that
he may share my research and offer me his insights.
Do this thing for me, and bring back what he gives you,

09f27693-ebaa-4db0-aee8-1055e064817a.title: Sedridor
09f27693-ebaa-4db0-aee8-1055e064817a.text:
and if my suspicions are correct, I will let you into the
knowledge of one of the greatest secrets this world has
ever known! A secret so powerful that it destroyed the

492a1d60-2409-4aeb-a5ac-8926411051b8.title: Sedridor
492a1d60-2409-4aeb-a5ac-8926411051b8.text:
original Wizards' Tower all of those centuries
ago! My research, combined with this mysterious
talisman... I cannot believe the answer to
the mysteries is so close now!

c56c34c2-4045-434a-83da-6a43cf6d3fbd.title: Sedridor
c56c34c2-4045-434a-83da-6a43cf6d3fbd.text:
Do this thing for me <player>. Be rewarded in a
way you can never imagine.

a81318bb-abea-4931-8683-2c46a2639cea.title: Sedridor
a81318bb-abea-4931-8683-2c46a2639cea.text:
As you wish adventurer. I will continue to study this
talisman you have brought me. Return here if you find
yourself with some spare time to help me.

25c1f15d-d9cf-444e-86a3-a80f18ea558c.title: Sedridor
25c1f15d-d9cf-444e-86a3-a80f18ea558c.text:
Take this package, and head directly North
from here, through Draynor village, until you reach
the Barbarian Village. Then head East from there
until you reach Varrock.

ee53b9de-0603-4a06-9587-e7938f761a64.title: Sedridor
ee53b9de-0603-4a06-9587-e7938f761a64.text:
Once in Varrock, take this package to the owner of the
rune shop. His name is Aubury. You may find it
helpful to ask one of Varrock's citizens for directions,

eaffe93f-524e-46ca-a2bd-ae923e392bbc.title: Sedridor
eaffe93f-524e-46ca-a2bd-ae923e392bbc.text:
as Varrock can be a confusing place for the first time
visitor. He will give you a special item - bring it back to
me, and I shall show you the mystery of the runes...

93b6eba3-9893-4f89-849b-1f27b2a9ef8c.title: Sedridor
93b6eba3-9893-4f89-849b-1f27b2a9ef8c.text: Best of luck with your quest, <player>.

6a150a5f-0aeb-4fe2-bd36-ff05fb2d6ed1.title: Sedridor
6a150a5f-0aeb-4fe2-bd36-ff05fb2d6ed1.text:
Welcome adventurer, to the world renowned
Wizards' Tower. How may I help you?

d1691375-9114-4a0b-bc08-cfecf32dde9b.title: Sedridor
d1691375-9114-4a0b-bc08-cfecf32dde9b.text:
Ah, <player>. How goes your quest? Have you
delivered the research notes to my friend Aubury yet?

f3868bd0-f804-453e-b7ea-31662a4004ce.title: Sedridor
f3868bd0-f804-453e-b7ea-31662a4004ce.text:
Well, please do so as soon as possible. Remember: to get
to Varrock, head due North, through Draynor Village,
around Draynor Manor, and then head East when

b011c9ec-8f6d-4792-a562-79242efa6c62.title: Sedridor
b011c9ec-8f6d-4792-a562-79242efa6c62.text:
you get to the Barbarian village. The man you seek
is named Aubury, and he owns the rune shop there.
It is vital he receives this package.

321af47d-3b72-43b9-95cf-280612d422b2.title: Sedridor
321af47d-3b72-43b9-95cf-280612d422b2.text:
Welcome adventurer, to the world renowned
Wizards' Tower. How may I help you?

5fd4c2c0-0c5d-4035-940d-45811713e3f0.title: Sedridor
5fd4c2c0-0c5d-4035-940d-45811713e3f0.text:
Ah, <player>. How goes your quest? Have you
delivered the research notes to my friend Aubury yet?

7ae5705a-9545-4e6e-9860-49ca70ff2c7c.title: <player>
7ae5705a-9545-4e6e-9860-49ca70ff2c7c.text:
Yes, I have. He gave me some research notes
to pass on to you.

4c325784-241b-4b15-958a-b513fb4766da.title: Sedridor
4c325784-241b-4b15-958a-b513fb4766da.text: May I have his notes then?

a5402b88-28f5-4b1f-be91-f4ab667d7e80.title: Sedridor
a5402b88-28f5-4b1f-be91-f4ab667d7e80.text:
Well, before you hand them over to me, as you
have been nothing but truthful with me to this point,
and I admire that in an adventurer, I will let you
into the secret of our research.

7d7e3d0e-5297-4b39-a423-0f17e68bc08f.title: Sedridor
7d7e3d0e-5297-4b39-a423-0f17e68bc08f.text:
Now as you may or may not know, many
centuries ago, the wizards at this Tower
learnt the secret of creating Rune Stones, which
allowed us to cast Magic very easily.

4009c285-b91c-46e9-bca8-09eea1de13c5.title: Sedridor
4009c285-b91c-46e9-bca8-09eea1de13c5.text:
When this Tower was burnt down the secret of
creating runes was lost to us for all time... except it
wasn't. Some months ago, while searching these ruins
for information from the old days,

52d6a1ff-4a96-4d83-a40c-6343db4bdfc8.title: Sedridor
52d6a1ff-4a96-4d83-a40c-6343db4bdfc8.text:
I came upon a scroll, almost destroyed, that detailed a
magical rock deep in the icefields of the North, closed
off from access by anything other than magical means.

cc302a9f-ac56-4a98-b8e1-84c40b78f3c2.title: Sedridor
cc302a9f-ac56-4a98-b8e1-84c40b78f3c2.text:
This rock was called the 'Rune Essence' by the
magicians who studied its powers. Apparently, by simply
breaking a chunk from it, a Rune Stone could be
fashioned very quickly and easily at certain

a4457b53-ac6e-4dc6-b478-9dc7eb64be56.title: Sedridor
a4457b53-ac6e-4dc6-b478-9dc7eb64be56.text:
elemental altars that were scattered across the land
back then. Now, this is an interesting little piece of
history, but not much use to us as modern wizards
without access to the Rune Essence,

14b8d5d8-cb14-4aab-80e4-d41f53250779.title: Sedridor
14b8d5d8-cb14-4aab-80e4-d41f53250779.text:
or these elemental altars. This is where you and
Aubury come into this story. A few weeks back,
Aubury discovered in a standard delivery of runes
to his store, a parchment detailing a

1d0f047e-7ca4-4f68-91e6-dc6a8ab7a16b.title: Sedridor
1d0f047e-7ca4-4f68-91e6-dc6a8ab7a16b.text:
teleportation spell that he had never come across
before. To his shock, when cast it took him to a
strange rock he had never encountered before...
yet that felt strangely familiar...

93e395d3-219a-44c7-ba45-d324ac645bd0.title: Sedridor
93e395d3-219a-44c7-ba45-d324ac645bd0.text:
As I'm sure you have now guessed, he had discovered a
portal leading to the mythical Rune Essence. As soon as
he told me of this spell, I saw the importance of his find,

eddb5eb0-4aed-480c-8133-c825bcca16ce.title: Sedridor
eddb5eb0-4aed-480c-8133-c825bcca16ce.text:
for if we could but find the elemental altars spoken
of in the ancient texts, we would once more be able
to create runes as our ancestors had done! It would
be the saviour of the wizards' art!

148a2e36-3e51-4490-b11b-6171d5c99b3a.title: <player>
148a2e36-3e51-4490-b11b-6171d5c99b3a.text:
I'm still not sure how I fit into
this little story of yours...

a3a4f89b-a1a8-4cbb-9e40-653d45ce5340.title: Sedridor
a3a4f89b-a1a8-4cbb-9e40-653d45ce5340.text:
You haven't guessed? This talisman you brought me...
it is the key to the elemental altar of air! When
you hold it next, it will direct you towards

f5440e2a-69fa-487a-909a-ab407a856174.title: Sedridor
f5440e2a-69fa-487a-909a-ab407a856174.text:
the entrance to the long forgotten Air Altar! By
bringing pieces of the Rune Essence to the Air Temple,
you will be able to fashion your own Air Runes!

044e1dc5-09de-4728-a602-5223061576ea.title: Sedridor
044e1dc5-09de-4728-a602-5223061576ea.text:
And this is not all! By finding other talismans similar
to this one, you will eventually be able to craft every
rune that is available on this world! Just

919f9687-31fa-4c61-a9fc-b707b570a0af.title: Sedridor
919f9687-31fa-4c61-a9fc-b707b570a0af.text:
as our ancestors did! I cannot stress enough what a
find this is! Now, due to the risks involved of letting
this mighty power fall into the wrong hands

284d06d9-df26-4c0b-b5ae-aefde0e2f5d9.title: Sedridor
284d06d9-df26-4c0b-b5ae-aefde0e2f5d9.text:
I will keep the teleport skill to the Rune Essence
a closely guarded secret, shared only by myself
and those Magic users around the world
whom I trust enough to keep it.

8a209701-0212-4d9f-99db-6c9e78ae005b.title: Sedridor
8a209701-0212-4d9f-99db-6c9e78ae005b.text:
This means that if any evil power should discover
the talismans required to enter the elemental
temples, we will be able to prevent their access
to the Rune Essence and prevent

26fcbf7d-adbc-4c4c-8241-0a602d69f5de.title: Sedridor
26fcbf7d-adbc-4c4c-8241-0a602d69f5de.text:
tragedy befalling this world. I know not where the
temples are located, nor do I know where the talismans
have been scattered to in this land, but I now

bd78c27c-759e-4ae0-9492-d38211348f4a.title: Sedridor
bd78c27c-759e-4ae0-9492-d38211348f4a.text:
return your Air Talisman to you. Find the Air
Temple, and you will be able to charge your Rune
Essences to become Air Runes at will. Any time

81a96797-9b92-4e42-ac66-c78fcd1b0aec.title: Sedridor
81a96797-9b92-4e42-ac66-c78fcd1b0aec.text:
you wish to visit the Rune Essence, speak to me
or Aubury and we will open a portal to that
mystical place for you to visit.

d0904160-f2b3-4cb7-99be-685f8b172505.title: <player.
d0904160-f2b3-4cb7-99be-685f8b172505.text:
So only you and Aubury know the teleport
spell to the Rune Essence?

c557c603-71bd-43a7-a020-fbc560139259.title: Sedridor
c557c603-71bd-43a7-a020-fbc560139259.text:
No... there are others... whom I will tell of your
authorisation to visit that place. When you speak
to them, they will know you, and grant you
access to that place when asked.

76424a4a-5daf-421a-bbf5-9d769733dc7f.title: Sedridor
76424a4a-5daf-421a-bbf5-9d769733dc7f.text:
Use the Air Talisman to locate the air temple,
and use any further talismans you find to locate
the other missing elemental temples.
Now... my research notes please?

a0a8dc7b-d405-4fc3-bf77-5a5f9ecf7438.title: Sedridor
a0a8dc7b-d405-4fc3-bf77-5a5f9ecf7438.text: Return to me once you have.

b6af2134-57f7-4f5a-88d3-72f880358caf.title: Sedridor
b6af2134-57f7-4f5a-88d3-72f880358caf.text:
Welcome adventurer, to the world renowned
Wizards' Tower. How may I help you?

304227ef-1382-4a13-93d6-8c94b59d90c3.title: Sedridor
304227ef-1382-4a13-93d6-8c94b59d90c3.text: Hello again <player>. What can I do for you?

options.text: Nothing thanks, I'm just looking around.
Can you teleport me to the Rune Essence?

6627804b-f85e-4eb7-af69-9c65c4f7101c.title: <player>
6627804b-f85e-4eb7-af69-9c65c4f7101c.text: Nothing thanks, I'm just looking around.

f696949e-de0d-42ef-9e19-fd75e3cdc721.title: Sedridor
f696949e-de0d-42ef-9e19-fd75e3cdc721.text:
Well, take care adventurer. You stand on the
ruins of the old destroyed Wizards' Tower.
Strange and powerful magicks lurk here.

6f39605e-0654-4f25-ab88-eb3dcb29720c.title: <player>
6f39605e-0654-4f25-ab88-eb3dcb29720c.text: Can you teleport me to the Rune Essence?
